transformers.min.js
  Library: @huggingface/transformers 4.2.0 (Transformers.js)
  License: Apache-2.0
  URL: https://github.com/huggingface/transformers.js
  Note: at runtime the library downloads model weights from the
        Hugging Face Hub and, on first use, the onnxruntime-web WASM
        runtime from jsDelivr (its built-in default; pinned to the
        onnxruntime-web version bundled in this file). Both are cached
        by the browser afterwards.

web-llm.js
  Library: @mlc-ai/web-llm 0.2.84 (WebLLM / MLC LLM)
  License: Apache-2.0
  URL: https://github.com/mlc-ai/web-llm
  Note: at runtime the library downloads model weights from the
        Hugging Face Hub and compiled WebGPU model libraries (wasm)
        from the MLC binary distribution; both are cached by the
        browser afterwards.

